data.description: Do not miss this Turn-key incredible townhouse. Enjoy this spacious and completely renovated home with brand new SPC luxury vinyl flooring throughout the house with new modern baseboards, new 2024 electrical panel and exterior electrical surge protector, new appliances in the whole kitchen, new ceiling high hats lighting and light fixtures, brand new toilets and vanities in all 3 bathrooms, A/C ducts and unit have been professionally serviced and cleaned with a smart Thermostat, new curtains, freshly painted walls and all doors. Just minutes away from Baptist Hospital, the Turnpike, and restaurants. Act now; as this gorgeous home will not last.
